
// This Hyperlambda code changes the value of all [status] nodes located under the [staff] nodes within the [company] node to "active". The [set-value] slot is used to update the value of nodes, and its expression targets all [status] nodes that are descendants of [staff] nodes, which are themselves descendants of the [company] node.
set-value:x:@.company/*/staff/*/*/status
   .:active
